#### 9. List the different kinds of javascript loops and describe what they do.

//Your Answer

//Googled Answer
for - loops through a block of code a number of times
for/in - loops through the properties of an object
while - loops through a block of code while a specified condition is true
do/while - also loops through a block of code while a specified condition is true

#### 10. How would you explain "scope" in javascript?

//Your Answer
scope is like how something is able to be viewed within the file. There is Global and local scope. global will allow you to see it throughout the entire whereas local scope is going to be limited to the area in which you enclose it.
//Googled Answer



